isValid

boolean isValid()
If true, the trace & span ID are both valid (i.e., non-zero).

These are a few common reasons for why you may be unable to get a valid trace context:

  • No OneAgent is present, or it is incompatible with this SDK version (check OneAgentSDK.getCurrentState())
  • There is no currently active PurePath context.
  • Some other reason; more information may be available through OneAgentSDK.setLoggingCallback(com.dynatrace.oneagent.sdk.api.LoggingCallback)
